    "description": "Tales of the Vagabond is a Third Person Action Adventure Game set in the fantasy world of Midland. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/a0180f9f5a9f15a8db783cb347bebe78.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=334 /></span><br><br>Midland is a world filled with danger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/b5399eb988fb07c4198b9c87dd62d4b1.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>You must be able to fight well. Lock-on to your target, parry, riposte, backstab and dodge roll.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/f6e49486dfd4f209128badd7befc37b7.poster.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/f6e49486dfd4f209128badd7befc37b7.webm?t=1678137272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/f6e49486dfd4f209128badd7befc37b7.mp4?t=1678137272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the world. Swim, fish, hunt and forage. Be able to live off the land. Survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/a020724bac8ba62d0be3ef808f4a320f.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>Go to town and interact with NPCs, get information, buy and sell food and equipment, repair weapons and armor, accept quests or just rest your head for the night.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/47e3f4803bd46e66287159a8b6f968dc.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>Equip yourself. Vary your loadout to give you the best chances to succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/9517da7415fb15c887873f5152ae3e7b.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>Take on dynamic quests that change objectives and rewards from session to session.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318640/extras/6610a6f10c722e41e6cdd9f9aa3a3ab4.avif?t=1678137272\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>The many tales of the vagabond are yours to tell.",
